xxl.core.indexStructures.rtrees

Class TGSBulkLoader<T>

  • java.lang.Object
    • xxl.core.indexStructures.rtrees.AbstractIterativeRtreeBulkloader<T>
      • xxl.core.indexStructures.rtrees.TGSBulkLoader<T>
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    IterativeBulkLoaderInterface<T>

    public class TGSBulkLoader<T>
extends AbstractIterativeRtreeBulkloader<T>
    This is an implementation of TGS R tree loading approach: Yvan J. Garcia R, Mario A. Lopez and Scott T. Leutenegger A greedy algorithm for bulk loading R-trees Note: This is an experimental version. This loading implementation is conducted in main memory.
